Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.91,0:00:13.70,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it when I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:19.62,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Nijika and her friends made them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.23,0:00:23.62,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,But the typhoon still came in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:28.05,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not like rain charms \Nactually affect the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:32.18,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,Even the people who bought tickets \Nmight not come at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:37.36,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they're not too \Nheartbroken by the small crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:40.43,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,They practiced so hard for this. \NI feel bad for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:44.98,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Real bands get screwed over \Nby life all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:49.28,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,They need to learn to make it \Nthrough any situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:52.05,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:53.61,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:56.99,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H484936&\pos(320,198.5)}Tickets go on sale at {\c&H20665f&}5 pm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:59.47,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like my friends can't come either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:01.03,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Same with my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.03,0:01:04.40,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,M-My grandma was supposed \Nto look after Futari,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:06.48,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,b-but now she can't come, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:09.58,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Makes sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:12.84,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Our audience is going to be\Nless than half of what we expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:14.58,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.58,0:01:15.67,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take it in stride!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:18.00,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:18.68,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Nijika-chan always stays so cheerful, \Nno matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:24.52,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, look alive there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:27.11,DefaultTop,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's the low-pressure system. So sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:28.52,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Even during the concert \Nwhere I was just helping...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:32.40,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She worked so hard to cheer me up \Nwhen I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:33.55,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:36.40,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,For today's concert...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:41.74,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\fad(238,1)\an8\c&H283031&\3c&HF9F9F3&}Sergeant for a Day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.85,0:01:38.41,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring the hype!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:40.61,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan, this is a serious concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:41.74,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,No messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:43.87,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You really like that outfit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:45.19,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:49.17,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, look at that rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.85,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan, I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:53.26,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,M-Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:55.60,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you came here for Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:58.55,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yeah! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:00.68,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:03.81,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,She was my junior in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:07.31,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Betcher havin' an afterparty tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:09.56,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Picked an izakaya yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:09.56,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,You reek of booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:13.09,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I know a good one, 'kay? 'Kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:16.35,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,How did you become even {\i1}more{\i0} \Nof a pain in the ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:20.20,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,She's as annoying as a college student \Nwho just learned about drinking parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:22.97,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,And look at you! You're soaked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:25.45,Default,Fan 1,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:27.50,Default,Fan 2,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.07,0:02:29.79,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The girls from our street concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.55,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You really came?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:33.54,Default,Fan 2,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:36.37,Default,Fan 2,0000,0000,0000,,We're your fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:39.88,Default,Fan 1,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be expecting a performance \Npowerful enough to blow away the typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:49.67,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Fans...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:52.80,Default,Fan 1,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You {\i1}are{\i0} Hitori-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:54.11,Default,Fan 2,0000,0000,0000,,Did we have the wrong person?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:56.05,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,My fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:59.86,DefaultItalics,Mai-kun/Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats! Congrats! Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.35,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,My fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:07.00,Default,Fan 1/Fan 2,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}is{\i0} the wrong person!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:13.85,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the rain's \Nonly going to get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:15.26,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Worse than {\i1}this{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:16.52,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:18.71,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should just stream it \Nas a no-audience concert
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:21.35,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,and act like it was supposed \Nto be that way from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:22.80,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We're not doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:24.65,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's way too late to get anyone to tune in,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:26.72,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,and we've already got a couple people here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.60,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I-It'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:36.82,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A-As long as we have p-people \Nwaiting to see us p-perform!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:40.07,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs30\b1\c&H3844BE&\3c&HD1DEE8&\bord2\pos(320,74)}Ripe Mangos
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:38.44,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.99,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She's evolved somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:40.11,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs30\b1\c&H3844BE&\3c&HD1DEE8&\bord2\pos(320,74)\clip(227,30,339,101.5)}Ripe Mangos
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:40.15,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs30\b1\c&H3844BE&\3c&HD1DEE8&\bord2\pos(320,74)\clip(226,27,268,84.5)}Ripe Mangos
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:47.20,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It's just about start time, and there's \Nreally not many people out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:49.55,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But the other bands' fans are here too,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:51.05,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm sure they'll all listen to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:54.41,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure more will arrive if we start.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:57.83,Default,Audience A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you ever heard of this \Nfirst group? Kessoku Band?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.85,Default,Audience B,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know. Don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:01.30,Default,Audience A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, seems like a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:09.15,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, we're new, \Nso of course no one knows us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:10.13,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it get you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:11.76,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,E-Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:13.41,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it. Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:14.81,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:17.74,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, it's almost time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:20.20,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that concert, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:40.84,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,A pleasure to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.33,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,We're Kessoku Band!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:47.15,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,We appreciate your kind attendance \Nin spite of this awful weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:51.93,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan, that's way too polite \Nfor a rock band!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.26,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I want my mango box!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:58.03,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I want to disappear altogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:59.77,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get to that first song!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:03.26,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Please lend your ears to our original song:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:05.60,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,"Guitar, Solitude, and the Blue Planet"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:22.51,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,A sudden evening shower falls
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:26.20,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,And yeah, it figures, \NI don't have an umbrella...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:30.23,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares how the sky's feeling, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:33.22,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,When it's time for the seasons to change
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:36.01,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What are you supposed to wear? Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:38.15,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Nijika-chan's drumming feels a little slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:39.98,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Spring and fall... yeah, where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:44.86,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,The pressure of information, suffocating
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:44.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And Kita-san's making mistakes \Nshe didn't make in practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:47.51,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,A spiral of vertigo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:48.31,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-san and Nijika-chan \Naren't in sync at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:49.91,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know where I am
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:56.16,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear myself breathing \Nso loud, so loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:06:01.29,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But why? I can't hear the \Nsounds of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:05.40,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It's not enough, not enough, \NNo one knows I'm here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:10.89,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I screamed when I couldn't \Nmake a scribble of a sound
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:10.89,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,We're not playing the way we usually do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:15.55,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I supposed to show "just who I am" to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:20.56,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm singing just like the fool I am
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:24.17,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's lay it all out to the stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:49.22,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,That was "Guitar, Solitude, \Nand the Blue Planet"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.52,Default,Audience A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:53.62,Default,Audience B,0000,0000,0000,,We should've showed up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.19,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:57.70,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan, you need to \Nintroduce the next song!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:58.96,Default,KIta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:01.29,Default,KIta,0000,0000,0000,,The next is another of our original songs,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:03.36,DefaultTop,KIta,0000,0000,0000,,and it's one we just wrote...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:05.82,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Our performance and\Nour songs still aren't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:12.41,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.37,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to let it stay this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:59.83,Songs_Insert,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That band's songs sound to me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:05.42,Songs_Insert,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,like shrill laughter all around
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:10.00,Songs_Insert,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That band's songs are to me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:15.82,Songs_Insert,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,like the piercing clang of a railway crossing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:21.48,Songs_Insert,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push me forward
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:24.90,Songs_Insert,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,There's a train coming
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:27.44,Songs_Insert,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.73,Songs_Insert,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,There's a halo in the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:32.49,Songs_Insert,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I cover my ears
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:34.85,Songs_Insert,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,There's a steady beating pulse within
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:37.69,Songs_Insert,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Deep in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:39.79,Songs_Insert,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,My heart makes my body sway
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:42.70,Songs_Insert,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear anything else
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:46.58,Songs_Insert,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing but the sounds I'm making
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.11,Default,Audience A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:18.87,Default,Audience B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.95,Default,Fan 1,0000,0000,0000,,That was super cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:23.75,Default,Fan 2,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.96,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Magnificent smugface.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:41.05,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,That was our second song, "That Band"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:43.72,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Now, here's our last song!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:48.73,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\an8\fnTimes New Roman\c&H83C3EF&\3c&H2C4253&}Kaomise
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.15,Default,Nijika/Ryo/Kita/Seika/Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.15,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.36,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Nice work on the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:54.80,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,This is all on my tab, so drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:57.85,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sis! Though we don't drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:59.96,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Love ya, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:02.47,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,You pay your own way. Get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:04.70,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Who exactly is this woman, if I may ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:09.97,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Genius bassist and unparalleled \Nbass-lover, Kikuri Hiroi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:12.49,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I left my bass at a drinking party yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:14.71,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,but I forgot which drinking party, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:16.91,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Instant self-contradiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:18.87,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I've been to a lot of your concerts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:21.60,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, for real? You got good taste, hon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:23.85,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You spray booze on the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:27.55,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Blind drunk concerts are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:29.39,Flashback,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, forgot the words!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:32.06,Flashback,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, that's how concerts go sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.86,Flashback,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be mad, you jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:36.78,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I treasure my memory of \Nyou stepping on my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:39.06,Flashback,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Shinjuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:42.12,Flashback,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I love you mother******s!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:46.47,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much about rock \NI have yet to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:49.52,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It might be okay not to learn all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:52.70,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Glad your concert turned out well in the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:54.83,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,For an audience of ten, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:58.31,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,But every single one of 'em left happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:10:59.38,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, guess so!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:03.05,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, keep it up, and you'll pick up fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:05.82,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Work hard for your next concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:07.57,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,And make sure you pay your quota fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:10.35,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be really inspiring \Nwithout the last bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:13.86,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,You worked really hard today too, \NBocchi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:16.08,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why's she a husk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:18.24,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan, don't turn to ash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.11,DefaultItalics,Bocchi,0000,0000,0000,,I've grown so tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:22.20,DefaultItalics,Mic-kun & Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats! Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.60,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,That's the wrong show!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:25.87,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, order as much food as you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:27.42,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.84,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Watcha gettin', Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:32.28,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of ordering karaage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:33.33,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sounds good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.82,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:36.80,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But this looks pretty good too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:37.26,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Isstagramming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.04,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the minister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:40.13,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:42.95,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,What do you like so much about that, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:43.64,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:46.93,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's like \Ngiving people a piece of the fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:49.73,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't everything more fun when \Nyou share it with your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:50.56,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(771,1)\bord1.2\fnComic Sans MS\pos(206.5,72)\c&HDFFEFF&\3c&H6095E4&\b0}Kit-aura
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:50.72,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Kit-aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:12:02.15,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1.2\fnComic Sans MS\move(206.5,72,336.67,72.8,24,525)\c&HDFFEFF&\3c&H6095E4&\b0}Kit-aura
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:51.90,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:55.35,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Use that Kita-chan power of yours \Nto purge my sister's twisted spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:56.55,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Twisted?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:58.49,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But the manager's really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:02.15,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(771,1)\bord1.2\fnComic Sans MS\c&HDFFEFF&\3c&H6095E4&\pos(486.5,288)\b0}Kit-aura
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:02.15,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(771,1)\bord1.2\fnComic Sans MS\c&HDFFEFF&\3c&H6095E4&\pos(154,278)\b0}Kit-aura
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:11:59.79,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Kit-aura! Kit-aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:00.70,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:01.57,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,You're killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:05.23,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've made up my mind. Here's the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:06.54,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:09.51,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:13.02,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have the avocado and \Ncream cheese pinchos!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:17.52,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,And the Spanish omelette \Nwith hollandaise sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:18.26,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,The what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:21.16,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Here! The omelette with hollandaise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:22.79,DefaultTop,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Hollanda-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:26.09,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-san's so fluent in trendy gibberish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:23.88,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:26.09,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Keep ordering!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:30.02,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she can casually\Nwalk into a Starpucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:32.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she could make the most complicated \Norders like it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:36.13,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a short puri-puri pepero \Npapipupepo peroppe pacina!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.63,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Kit-aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:39.59,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:40.29,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:42.80,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I w-won't be the way I usually am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:44.91,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make a trendy choice too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:46.07,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.63,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, I'll have the M-Machu Picchu Ruins,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:52.62,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Mississippi River, \NGrand Canyon San Diego hash...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:56.08,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,M-Machu Picchu, Machu Picchu, Machu Picchu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.13,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Where's that exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:12:59.81,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I read it wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:01.11,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I meant fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:02.63,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,How did you read that wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:04.27,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Pickled fish offals for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:06.32,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,How old're you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:08.76,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,You're already moving on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:12.01,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Izakayas are like my home ground, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:13.79,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how do you read this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:15.27,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first time at an izakaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:16.42,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Which one? I don't think \NI can read it either...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:18.20,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,but they're actually kind of fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:19.32,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You're so knowledgeable, Ryo-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:23.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they'll be even more fun\Nwhen I grow up and can drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:27.11,Default,Salaryman A,0000,0000,0000,,My wife's taste in clothing \Nchanged all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:30.33,Default,Salaryman A,0000,0000,0000,,And she suddenly started \Nlocking her smartphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:32.56,Default,Salaryman B,0000,0000,0000,,What, you check your wife's phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:35.20,Default,Salaryman A,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just happened to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:37.93,Default,Salaryman B,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like cheating to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:39.75,Default,Salaryman A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, gotta be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.70,Default,Salaryman A,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe I deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:45.19,Default,Salaryman A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so busy with work every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.19,0:13:46.84,Default,Salaryman B,0000,0000,0000,,You don't deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:50.92,Default,Salaryman A,0000,0000,0000,,Hours of unpaid overtime, forced to spend \Nmy days off golfing with clients...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:53.84,Default,Salaryman A,0000,0000,0000,,And when I do get an early break, \NI have such a hard time facing her
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:55.60,Default,Salaryman A,0000,0000,0000,,I go drinking with you instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:58.47,Default,Salaryman A,0000,0000,0000,,What am I even doing all this work for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:00.36,Default,Salaryman B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you all right, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:05.40,Default,Salaryman A,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I look at the station platform, and\NI find myself about to jump onto the tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.63,Default,Salaryman B,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, have some more to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:08.25,Default,Salaryman B,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! More shochu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.99,Default,Bar Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing! One shochu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:13.79,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Is life just an unrelenting hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:16.32,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't make my stage \Ndebut in high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:19.60,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have to get a proper career too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:24.18,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not smart enough to get into college,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:24.96,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,96)\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\fs16\c&HADC6C0&\3c&H443D87&\frz27.17\pos(356,273.5)}Fail to make debut,\N get a job
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:27.42,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,554)\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\fs16\c&H2D2C35&\3c&H6DA9BB&\frz357.6\pos(268,111)}Graduate high school
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:27.42,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,554)\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\fs16\c&H2D2C35&\3c&H6DA9BB&\pos(247,149.5)\frz6.864}Move on to college
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:27.68,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't even know what I'd go for...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:33.68,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(278,1)\fnComic Sans MS\fs16\c&H666962&\pos(312,91.5)\b0\bord2\3c&HF9FAF8&}Sales Results for December
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:33.68,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(278,1)\fnComic Sans MS\fs16\c&H666962&\b0\bord2\3c&HF9FAF8&\pos(171.5,129.5)}Target: 100
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:33.68,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fad(278,1)\fnComic Sans MS\fs16\c&H666962&\b0\bord2\3c&HF9FAF8&\pos(152,165)}Gotoh            Ozaki            Hasegawa         Koizumi           Ogawa
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:33.68,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fad(278,1)\fnComic Sans MS\fs16\c&H666962&\b0\bord2\3c&HF9FAF8&\pos(163.5,277)}5th              4th                  {\alpha&HFF&}3rd{\alpha&H00&}                2nd                 1st
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.90,0:14:33.68,Default,Superior,0000,0000,0000,,Your sales for this month were the \Nlowest on the team, Gotoh-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.74,Default,Colleague 1,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.57,Default,Colleague 2,0000,0000,0000,,It's partly the boss being cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:41.19,Default,Colleague 2,0000,0000,0000,,He transferred her to sales \Nto try to make her quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.94,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs14\3c&H7F7877&\c&H232623&\bord2\pos(320,239)\frx26\fry0}Tokoroten
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:44.09,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:46.53,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,W-Would you like to buy some tokoroten?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:48.56,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's well-aged, and it goes down smooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:49.86,Default,Solicited Man,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:54.87,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1572,1)\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\fs16\c&HB0C8C1&\3c&H55569D&\pos(559,126)}Transferred to\Nsales department
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:54.87,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1572,1)\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\fs16\c&HB0C8C1&\3c&H55569D&\pos(559,210.5)}Fail at door-\Nto-door sales
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:54.87,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1572,1)\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\fs16\c&HB0C8C1&\3c&H55569D&\pos(559,308.5)}Stress quit and\N become a shut-in
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:54.87,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I see as plain as day \Nwhere my Game of Life is going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:57.87,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori-chan, won't you open up? Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:00.37,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to go back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:02.87,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Just come eat dinner with me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:03.71,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:06.63,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\fnArial Black\fs40\c&H141416&\3c&HC4C4C4&\bord1\move(366,55,1200,55)\clip(m 309 1 l 355 62 420 153 640 170 640 2)}aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:09.68,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Another of Bocchi-chan's episodes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:12.39,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that {\i1}is{\i0} typical for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:15.02,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't make money with my guitar, \NI'll end up a NEET.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:16.97,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Her face is scary when it gets like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:16.97,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't make money with my guitar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:20.30,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I think it's got personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:21.48,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Are you for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.30,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Sandpaper, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:26.00,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of a chore, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:27.59,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops. Think I botched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.00,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.21,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it like this. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.24,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,They're used to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:33.90,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Up we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:35.93,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Did I make her face too long?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:38.21,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:40.34,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:44.63,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,A-Actually, can I fix it up a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:48.36,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Ikuyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:53.55,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You played pretty well today for only \Nhaving done this for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.76,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who's Ikuyo again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:02.78,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno! Who'd have a crummy \Nold name like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.15,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}your{\i0} name, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.49,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Kita-chan's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:09.00,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,That face is contagious, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:11.39,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I hid it for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:13.32,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I hate my name so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:15.41,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,How come? It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:18.39,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't understand, \Nsince you have a beautiful name
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:20.00,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,that means "song of the stars"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:21.37,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Look at her freak out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.78,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But mine sounds like a bad pun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:25.97,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,"Kita! Ikuyo!" (I'm here! Let's go!)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.37,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:29.84,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,I think we broke her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:33.66,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,My full name is Kita Kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:36.84,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing you withdraw into your shell is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:38.39,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,You're sadistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:41.59,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,So, as for what you were saying before...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:46.77,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,You were mumbling about supporting yourself \Nwith the guitar and becoming a NEET.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:49.20,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry for losing my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:51.36,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, nothin' wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:55.36,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,But lemme give you some advice \Nas your senpai in the world of bands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:58.49,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Just chill out and enjoy yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:03.41,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,If you put the weight of success \Non your own shoulders all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:05.28,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,you'll just make yourself miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.59,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:10.25,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,It's important to enjoy the process \Nof making your dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:14.98,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Senpai, how come \Nyou suddenly quit playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:17.68,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The manager was in a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:20.64,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yah. They were {\i1}super{\i0} popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.92,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Then wh-why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:24.85,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,I got sick of bands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:28.06,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,But you run a club. \NWhat's the deal there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.38,DefaultTop,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:31.26,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Nijika-chan never said a word about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:32.47,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,What, I can? Thanks a bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:35.53,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? And Nijika-chan's been gone a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:34.07,DefaultTop,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not paying for you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.53,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:37.84,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:39.45,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I have to use the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.70,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Manager, keep 'em comin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.63,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me... Nijika-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:53.64,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:55.59,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.34,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, just getting some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:01.79,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's been getting cold \Nat night lately, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:04.60,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Sure has.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:08.64,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Next thing we know, \Nsummer break's gonna be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:09.89,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I hear nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:11.23,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I know nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.84,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Summer break never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:14.56,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:17.70,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Trees, water, planets, Milky Way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.70,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan! Back to reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.35,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.46,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:26.08,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:28.83,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I realized something while I was \Nwatching you play today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:32.05,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You're guitarhero, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:39.98,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, a-actually, n-no, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:43.81,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It was pretty obvious from the \Non-point way you were strumming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:47.06,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,And I finally noticed \Nyou had the same guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:49.98,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,No use trying to hide it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:52.36,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.40,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:57.36,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I didn't hide it on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:02.24,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Since I'm anything but a hero right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:05.93,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I w-wanted to wait to tell you \Nuntil I fixed the way I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:09.12,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,E-Especially you, Nijika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:15.13,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you shocked to find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.42,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:19.30,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It made me all the more happy to have you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.01,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:25.31,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,See, I told you I had a dream before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.26,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:32.57,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,My mom died when I was little, \Nand my dad was never home,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:35.02,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,so my sister was pretty much my only family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:40.00,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But since I hated being alone, \Nwhen my sis started a band,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:42.79,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I had her take me to her clubs all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:47.58,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It all seemed so shining to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:50.14,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I was never happier anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:56.50,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I was her inspiration for quitting her band \Nand starting up this club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:20:02.01,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Starry is a place my sister made for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:05.39,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'll bet she won't admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:09.39,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,So my real dream
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:12.89,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,is to make a band popular \Nenough for me and my sister
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:16.52,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,and make Starry even more famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:20.44,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But when I actually started my band,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:24.45,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I spent a while thinking that \Nit was kind of out of my reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:27.71,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,And everyone was so disheartened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:33.33,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But every time things \Nare looking their worst,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:31.04,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs26\b1\c&H3844BE&\3c&HD1DEE8&\bord2\pos(328.5,113.5)}Ripe Mangos
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:36.97,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,you're the one who breaks through it for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:42.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan, you were \None heck of a hero to me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:49.26,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo wants to use this band to finally \Nget to play music from the heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:53.08,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,and Kita-chan wants to really \Ndo something with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:57.25,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,They've all invested their hopes in the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:04.66,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, you never actually told me \Nwhat you were doing the band for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.28,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:14.68,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,As a guitarist, I want to make the \NKessoku Band we all care so much about
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:16.50,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,the best band it can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:22.63,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A-And I want us to become such a popular band
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:25.15,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,that we can make money \Nand not have to finish school...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:27.99,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty tall order!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:29.34,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But I accept your investment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:37.52,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I sure do wish you could play the way \Nyou do in your videos every time, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:39.95,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll d-do my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.39,0:21:44.28,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But now I know it for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:47.70,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Having you with us will \Nmake our dreams possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:51.20,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,So keep showing us more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:52.95,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Of "Bocchi-chan's rock."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:56.53,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi the Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:04.96,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:06.99,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with not \Nletting my sound die down?
