Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:11.30,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with being young?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:10.89,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx93.53\t(27,2571,\fscx90.16)\fscy93.53\t(27,2571,\fscy90.16)\c&H07C7F0&\fnImpact\fs36\move(167.16,134.06,172.66,-51.94,27,2571)}BOCCHI THE ROCK!
