Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:20.14,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why doesn't it stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.31,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The rhythm that I can't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:25.99,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,keeps reverberating through my body
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:30.19,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The melody playing in my earphones
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.19,0:22:34.99,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,is the only thing that lets me be who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:39.20,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The sky is tinged in red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:45.00,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But what color is my soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:46.40,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:50.99,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:53.98,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been searching
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.98,0:22:57.20,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,for something precious (hey!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.20,0:23:02.82,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,If everything's going to be lost some day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.82,0:23:06.09,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,let's engrave it as deep as we can (now!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.09,0:23:09.50,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,My most pathetic nights \Nand cackling laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:13.68,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And days when I couldn't say \Nmore than "You know..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.68,0:23:17.84,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,(I'm alive now, yeah Springtime of life)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.84,0:23:19.77,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with not \Nletting my sound die down?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.77,0:23:23.86,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with being young?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.98,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(3572,1)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H41403D&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1\bord2\shad2\4c&H4700CE&\pos(309,49.5)}#09 Enoshima Escar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.62,0:23:39.98,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it!
